}

### Main step 2: check unupdated user name
GET /api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=


# Negative test: user cannot change his name with username contains $%^&*()@# characters
### Main step 1: change name to name with $%^&*()@# characters
PUT /api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

{
  "name": "$%^&*()@#"
}

### Main step 2: check unupdated user name
GET /api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=